Supply, Erection, Testing And Commissioning Of (i) 2 Nos. 220kv Bays At Proposed 220/132/33kv Chandanvally (tsiic) Ss (ii) 220kv Single Moose Dc Line (2.2 Km) From Proposed 220/132/33kv Chandanvally (tsiic) Ss To Proposed 220kv M/s. Amazon (chandanvally)

Tenders are invited for Supply, erection, testing and commissioning of (i) 2 nos. 220kv bays at proposed 220/132/33kv chandanvally (tsiic) ss (ii) 220kv single moose dc line (2.2 km) from proposed 220/132/33kv chandanvally (tsiic) ss to proposed 220kv m/s. amazon (chandanvally) ss on 220kv narrow based towers and (iii) 2 nos 220 kv bays at proposed 220kv m/s. amazon (chandanvally) ss including metering arrangements in shabad (m), ranga reddy district on turnkey basis Tender Category : Services OpeningDate : Jan 25 2022 12:00AM
